# pnpm hoist rules.
#
# `@types/*` packages must be visible to tsc in every workspace package that
# imports `node:*` modules — pangolin-core, pangolin-worker, pangolin-storage-local,
# pangolin-runtime-claude-code, etc. Without hoisting, each package would need
# its own explicit `@types/node` devDependency and the version drift surface
# would balloon. Public-hoisting the type packages keeps a single resolved
# version visible across the workspace, matching the de-facto behavior the
# local-dev environment already relied on via a globally-installed
# `@types/node`.
public-hoist-pattern[]=@types/*
